      <Nickname>Container</Nickname>
      <Description>$MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT - $MISSILESTAT_NONE - $MISSILESTAT_NONE</Description>
      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;CM-S-400 Container&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 4 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the CM-S-4 body, which is a heavy support torpedo.  This missile will deliver no payload.  It has no on-board targeting capability or seekers..

$MISSILESTAT_CONTROLMETHOD: $MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT
$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE: &lt;b&gt;&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_POS&lt;/color&gt;	&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_TRACK&lt;/color&gt;&lt;/b&gt;


$MISSILESTAT_SPEED: 125 $UNIT_METERSPERSEC
$MISSILESTAT_DISTANCE: 2,583 $UNIT_METERS
$MISSILESTAT_TOPSPEEDTIME: 0.7 $UNIT_SECONDS
$MISSILESTAT_TURNRATE: 4.0 $UNIT_GS
$MISSILESTAT_TERMINALS: None

$MISSILESTAT_HEALTH: 150 
$MISSILESTAT_WALLTHICKNESS: 0.2
$MISSILESTAT_PROGTIME: 20 $UNIT_SECONDS
$MISSILESTAT_RADARSIG: 100 %
$MISSILESTAT_BOOSTTIME: 3 $UNIT_SECONDS
$MISSILESTAT_BOOSTSTRAFE: 100 %
$MISSILESTAT_BOOSTTURN: 100 %
$MISSILESTAT_FAILRATE: 0 %</LongDescription>
